"好耐冇搞呢d，可能錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQ3<br />\nf(1) = 1/4<br />\nf'(x) = (3-x&sup2;)/(x&sup2;+3)&sup2;<br />\nSlope of g(x) =  f'(1) = (3-1&sup2;)/(1&sup2;+3)&sup2; = 2/16 = 1/8 <br />\nLet g(x) = (1/8)x + k <br />\nAs A = (1, f(1)), <br />\n1/4 = 1/8 + k <br />\nk = 1/8<br />\ng(x) =  (1/8)x + (1/8) = (x+1)/8<br />\n<br />\n跟住搵common point<br />\nx/(x&sup2;+3) =  (x+1)/8<br />\n8x = (x&sup2;+3)(x+1)<br />\n爆開<br />\nx&sup3;+x&sup2;-5x+3 =0 <br />\nFactorize<br />\n(x+3)(x-1)&sup2; = 0<br />\n兩個factor，所以兩個point<br />\n<br />\n其中一個x=1係題目俾<br />\n所以另一個就係x=-3 <br />\n<br />\nPart 2 畫出腸"},{"pid":"fad281d280f736d5405146ca6e4a8c11009bf22e","tid":2439834,"uid":209398,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"試做咗第1條<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要好熟quadratic equation/inequality, 同埋搵parametric family of curves pass through咩region呢種題型香港好少見所以無操過好易卡住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uoPpjov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuoPpjov.jpg&h=ff882cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RE43Qa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RE43Qa.jpg&h=bc0f82ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjh6xJv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffjh6xJv.jpg&h=3f918374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3339319f744ba38853412afa4b37ee1cf5d2f329","tid":2439834,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"其實唔難"},{"pid":"3f14aca314d6e5b6a9ae2ca02f1fcbcd9c1e67e4","tid":2439834,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f38375b5c1a5880c433c28c98423dbccaff7181","tid":2439834,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"同場加映東大英